protected static class AeWSBPELActivityScopeValidator.AeIsolatedScopeSearchVisitor
extends AeAbstractDefVisitor

Searches the enclosed scope's main branch to locate any isolated scopes that are targeted by a activity OR any isolated scopes if there was a found in a FCT handler.

isMatch

protected boolean isMatch(AeActivityScopeDef aActivityScopeDef)
Returns true if this scope is one that we're looking for, either because we're matching with a wildcard or it's targeted by a . If the wildcard is true, then we match all scopes. If the current level > 1, then we match all scopes since it means we must have traversed into a scope that we matched on. If the current level = 1, then we match on the scope if it's name is one of the ones we're looking for.

aActivityScopeDef -
